Last Broadcast Date: Fri 11 Jun 2010
On Outlook with Matthew Bannister... Life after a brutal attack British man Robert Maltby tells Matthew Bannister how he is coming to terms with the aftermath of an attack which left his girlfriend Sophie dead and him with brain damage. South African Buses In the second part of his series, Outlook's Mpho Lakaje has been on a journey with a woman and her daughter who are regular bus commuters. He hears how the new bus system in Johannesburg is controversial. Shark Attack Survivor We hear from Michael Bedford the Australian surfer who survived an attack by a great white shark. Show less